data.title: Building a Trusted Data Foundation for AI on Databricks - Data + AI Summit 2024
data.meta_description: For companies looking to leverage the power of AI at scale, modernizing data engineering is not a choice, it’s a requirement. Doing that right means having the ability to automate the discovery, integration, & transformation of source data directly into Databricks, while tapping into the Databricks AI Functions for advanced functionalities directly within workflows, making it easier to deploy AI-driven transformations and analysis. Learn how to Qlik integrates with Databricks AI Functions, and automates real-time complete end-to-end data pipelines that are low or no-code. Spend less time integrating and transforming data and more time performing rich AI driven analysis, LMM fine tuning, and feeding ML & generative AI models like Databricks DBRX. Join this session & learn how to Qlik Talend Data Integration automate the delivery and transformation of hundreds of sources of data, including SAP to the Databricks Intelligent Data Platform while reducing costs and latency.
